      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every aspect of the automobile\u2014from its pristine exterior finish to its factory-standard mechanical systems\u2014has been maintained with rigorous attention to detail. This is a definitive example of automotive excellence, offering an uncompromising driving experience for those who demand the highest caliber of quality and preservation.",
