    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 You have got to see this beauty! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly stunning condition and turns heads wherever it goes, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
