    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that remains in true showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin still carries the distinct scent of fresh leather; the bolsters show zero wear, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, with a full documented service history and zero modifications. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and silent. This is not just a well-kept car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
