      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of superlative caliber, this specimen represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, complemented by an interior that remains entirely free of wear or imperfection. Every mechanical component has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the most rigorous performance benchmarks. This is an acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
